# This folder contains API credentials for MCP servers
# ALL FILES IN THIS FOLDER ARE GITIGNORED

# Required credentials:

## Gmail / Google Sheets
# gmail.json - OAuth credentials from Google Cloud Console
# google.json - Same as gmail.json (copy it)

## Slack
# Set SLACK_BOT_TOKEN as environment variable instead

## Postgres
# Set DATABASE_URL as environment variable instead

# To add credentials:
# 1. Download from service provider
# 2. Save to this folder with correct filename
# 3. Never commit these files
